#: lib/webbkoll_web/templates/page/faq.html.eex:18
#, elixir-format
msgid "Profiling may additionally be used to shape political opinions, for instance through targeting specific groups with political information, or to enact measures against groups based on their assumed characteristics. This form of political work is called ”nudging” and may also be deployed to increase acceptance of specific measures (like the construction of a public park) in specific groups (such as the individuals living near the envisaged park)."
msgstr ""
"La profilazione può essere utilizzata anche per plasmare le opinioni "
